- Get a ring model. Duh!
- Create an internal and external texts. DuhÂ²!
Edit texts, size to around 5.000, Center/Middle alignment, word spacing to 10.000
- Use these modifiers on this order:
1- Solidifier - set to 0.8m
2- Remesh - set to 0.05 m
3- curve - curve object internal text, deform axis X; to external text use -X
Use the arrows to adjust scale and rotation

When applying everything, do not save!
Just keep as is to edit text keeping all configs.
- Convert text to mesh
- Apply boolean on text to ring
- Convert the ring with remesh to remove all no wanted vertices
- Export as .stl keeping selected and blender scale
